rComments: Don't let him scare you the first day when he claims how time-consuming the class is. He's a good teacher and i really enjoyed the class.
good teacher- you usually walk out of class wondering what the heck just happened, but it gets you to think. just know the main arguments and how they work.

Sarcastic, often seems mean about it, but it's his personality. Notes are totally written out for you. Overall okay class - just do some of the reading and take down the notes. Exams are essay style, but all questions are given BEFORE the exam so you can study them.
